{NORTH has 20 points and 4-4-3-2 distribution, so he opens 2NT.

SOUTH has 8 points. She adds NORTH's 20 or 21 for a total of 28 or 29, enough for game but 
nowhere close to the slam requirement. So she bids 3NT and NORTH passes.}

